  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Cantarell Fonts</title>
    <para>
      The <application>Cantarell</application> typeface family is
      a contemporary Humanist sans serif, and is used by the GNOME
      project for its user interface.
    </para>
    &lfs70_checked;
